node.text:
Based on your battery percentage, you will……
💚100-90% inherit an enchanted forest
💚89-80% become the next Jedi knight
💚79-70% Discover a doorway to Atlantis
💚69-60% Win free cookies for life
💚59-50% Have a free vacation anywhere you choose
💚49-40% go on a reading date with your favorite fictional character
💚39-30% turn into a werewolf
💚29-20% inherit Hades’ powers
💚19-10% Be granted 3 wishes
💚9-0% Be stuck at home with an unlimited book supply
-
Tag someone who’d want to live in this library 😍🌱📚🧡
-
Caption, animation & photoshop edit by @lulumoonowlbooks
